WAKE
"Evolution Through Extinction"

by Timothy Sibiski (aka "Asyranok")

Demo version 2.2; Published 2013

Genre: Science Fiction
Difficulty: Casual and Challenging pathways (both with unique story aspects and experience). Type command "Help" at any point to get a list of commands or general advice.
Category: Puzzle and Hidden Object

 There are native issues with timed-scripts in the online version. Please play the downloaded version for the full experience. If you do play the online version, please choose "Skip Intro" below. Thanks, and enjoy!

