You're at a crossroads. It looks as if there are multiple paths to choose from. If you make a decision, you will need to commit. There will be no turning back; although the paths may cross at some point.

(Your choices are...)

Streets: a challenging-difficulty pathway. If you choose to proceed, you will not be able to return and choose another path.

Sewers: a casual-difficulty pathway. If you choose to proceed, you will not be able to return and choose another path.
