> attempt reset Reactor Core

> attempt reset Reactor Core
Diagnostics run on your display.

"Processing...
Intention: System Reset

To initiate a reset, insert all of the fuel rods into their couplings.
Result: Controlled overload of reactor

Warning: Reactor overload will cause a reset of all facility systems. To continue with overload, reposition all rods into their couplings. To move rods, select specific rod and choose to "shift".

Reactor Core Error01: There is a malfunction in the executable files. Selecting a rod in column A will cause the adjacent rod in column B to shift.
Reactor Core Error02: There is a malfunction in the executable files. Selecting a rod in column B will cause the rod directly under it to shift."

